Mac-Tie-PList version 0.02
=================================

This module allows easy parsing of Apple PList (NSDictionary) objects, as
used in plist files.

Further details of NSDictionary's is available here:

	http://developer.apple.com/documentation/Cocoa/Reference/Foundation/ObjC_classic/Classes/NSDictionary.html

Note: Currently, read only fuctions are provided.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module is design for use on MacOS-X. It uses the objective C bridge
Foundation.pm as shipped with OS-X. The module intentionally uses only
modules shipped with Apple Perl distributions.

